# Proof of Value (PoV) Logic

## Description
This rule defines the implementation guidelines for the Proof of Value (PoV) system in Swarm.

## Globs
src/pov/**/*.ts

## Instructions

### Token System
- Mint SWARM tokens from Positive Values (likes), counter with Negative Values (dislikes)
- Lock tokens for 6 months, integrate bonding curve with kusd.koin
- Start with a simple PoV implementation, iterate based on feedback

### Implementation
- Use Koinos smart contracts via koilib for token distribution
- Ensure PoV logic is modular for future custom implementations
- Implement secure transaction handling and verification

### Integration
- Connect with AT Protocol for social actions (likes, reposts)
- Ensure proper error handling for blockchain interactions
- Implement caching for improved performance

